  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 10th level, you gain the <strong>Hunter's Revenge</strong> Defensive Tactic, if you didn't have it already. You may choose another Defensive Tactic if you already had Hunter's Revenge.</p><p>In addition, when you are hit by an attack from your <em><strong>Primary Target</strong></em>, the next time you deal your lethal attack damage to that creature your <em><strong>Lethal Attack</strong></em> die is increased by 1 step and you no longer need to meet the prerequisites of the Lethal Attack feature if your <em><strong>Primary Target</strong></em> has damaged you on this, or the previous round.</p>",
